title: Michael Jackson/The Jackson 5/The Jacksons Discography (new, com
description:
Over the years I`ve collected everything I could find of Michael Jackson / The Jackson 5 and The Jacksons.

Michael Jackson was probably the greatest entertainer of all time! He was an extraordinary singer, songwriter and dancer who influenced todays music in many ways. 

It takes a special person to touch so many people all over the globe! 

Music is a universal language and he spoke it fluently.
